  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposal, as a result of its positioning, would result in a loss of privacy for neighbouring dwellings as well as creating a source of noise disturbance for neighbouring dwellings contrary to LP2 &#x27;Development and Amenity&#x27; of the Hackney local plan and D6 &#x27;Housing Quality and Standards&#x27; of the London plan as well as the guidelines Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposal, as a result of its size and positioning, would result in a loss of outlook and increased sense of enclosure from neighbouring dwellings contrary to LP2 &#x27;Development and Amenity&#x27; of the Hackney local plan and D6 &#x27;Housing Quality and Standards&#x27; of the London plan as well as the guidelines Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed conservatory, by reason of its inappropriate scale, massing and location, would result in an unsympathetic and incongruous form of development to the detriment of the character and visual appearance of the application site and surrounding area, contrary to policy D4 &#x27;Delivering good design&#x27; of the London Plan (2021) as well as Policy LP1 &#x27;Design Quality and Local Character&#x27; of the Hackney Local Plan and the guidance contained within Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD 2009.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
